c         -> compose a new message
<shift>-r -> reply to the selected conversation
<shift>-a -> reply to all recipients
<shift>-f -> forward a conversation
<up>      -> display the previous message/conversation
<down>    -> display the next message/conversation
r         -> mark the message/conversation as read
u         -> mark the message/conversation as unread
*         -> mark the message/conversation as starred
t         -> move the message/conversation to trash
a         -> move the message/conversation to archive
s         -> move the message/conversation to spam


